Body:
m = GEKKO()
eq = m.Param(value=40)
x1, x2, x3, x4 = [m.Var() for i in range(4)]
x1.value = 1
x2.value = 5
x3.value = 5
x4.value = 1
x1.lower = 1
x2.lower = 1
x3.lower = 1
x4.lower = 1
x1.upper = 5
x2.upper = 5
x3.upper = 5
x4.upper = 5
m.Equation(x1 * x2 * x3 * x4 >= 25)
m.Equation(x1 ** 2 + x2 ** 2 + x3 ** 2 + x4 ** 2 == eq)
m.Obj(x1 * x4 * (x1 + x2 + x3) + x3)
m.options.IMODE = 3
m.solve(disp=False)
assert x1.value == [1.0]
assert x2.value == [4.743]
assert x3.value == [3.82115]
assert x4.value == [1.379408]
